    <note>Wang(2) Dingchen [3983] Based on generational name and chronological logic, I identify as a grandson of Wang(2) Li(2) [15706]. See also documentation for Zhu(1) Sun [521], Zhu(1) Mingzhi [526], Shen(2) Li [1452] and son-in-law, Zhu(1) Yanzhi [3266]. Subsequent identification in funerary inscription as son-in-law of Ding(1) Li [26502]] (q.v.), where he is identified as a Nanjing (i.e. Songzhou) person and where the funerary inscription for Ding(1) Li's father is designated as having been drafted by Wang(2) Yaochen, makes this identification nearly certain.</note>
